Subject: irqchip/gic-v3: Workaround Cavium erratum 38539 when reading
 GICD_TYPER2
Git-commit: d01fd161e85904064290435f67f4ed59af5daf74
Patch-mainline: v5.6-rc6
References: jsc#SLE-14773

